To ensure everyone stays together during your trip to Romania, consider these precautions:

* Travel and book accommodations together as a family;
* Visit unfamiliar areas with trusted locals beforehand;
* Inform a parent or guardian about your whereabouts and return time;
* Carry contact information for your family members;
* Keep addresses of places you plan on staying;
* Discuss and prepare a plan for possible separation scenarios.

